{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_51_01",
  "title": "白石千紗 1話 日頃の感謝を歌に乗せて",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』。アイドルがやっ\nてみたいことを叶えてくれる、雑誌のお誕生日企画かぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“Miracle ☆ Idol Birthday!” It’s that birthday project\nin the magazine where they grant wishes for idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.0024968646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.1666659037
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "私や沙季ちゃんに続いて\n千紗ちゃんにもお話が来たんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Following me and Saki-chan‚\nyou got an offer too‚ Chisa-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.2448314037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.7999998092
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "うん。でも、いざやることになったら\n何をお願いしようか悩んじゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. But now that I’m actually going to do it‚\nI’m having trouble deciding what to wish for…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.9923586118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 21.5999991734
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "良ければ、渚ちゃんとお姉ちゃんに\n相談したいなって思ったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I was hoping I could talk to\nNagisa-chan and you about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.2333325068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.0666668574
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことだったのね\n急に話があるって言うから、何かと思っちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that’s what it was.\nI was wondering what you want to talk about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.3666676204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.0179594994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、実際悩んじゃうよね\n私も、すぐには思いつかなかったな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s understandable that you’d be worried.\nI couldn’t think of anything right away either.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2846261661,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "私の時は、千紗がかわりに考えてくれたわよね\n好きなことを沢山させてもらえて、嬉しかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When it was my turn‚ Chisa thought of something for me.\nI was happy because I got to do a lot of things I liked.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1088694111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.7805219651
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗も難しく考えないで、お裁縫とか、ホラー映画とか\n好きなことに関係するお願いをするのはどうかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa‚ don’t overthink it. How about making a wish related to\nsomething you like‚ like sewing or horror movies?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.3666676204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.779864057
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.1537716651
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "そっか、好きなことで、やってみたいこと……\nあっ！　それなら私、ホラー映画に出てみたい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ something I like… something I want to do…\nAh! I know! I want to be in a horror movie!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1537716651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "制作が決まってる、『牛鳴きトンネル』の続編とか\n『妖怪へけへけ』の続編に出られたら、凄く嬉しいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like‚ the sequel to “Moo Tunnel” that’s in production‚ or the sequel to\n“Hekeheke Yokai.” It would be so cool to be in one of those~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.4650902829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.746531741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "ホラー映画に出演か～\n千紗ちゃんらしくて面白いんじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being in a horror movie‚ huh~?\nThat sounds like something you’d do‚ Chisa-chan. It’ll be fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.5608438553,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.7131984076
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "あ……でも、ホラー映画に出ることになったら\n雑誌の記事も、その撮影風景とかになっちゃうよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… but if I’m in a horror movie‚\nthe magazine article will be about the filming…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.4798650743,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.3798589708
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、映画が難しかったら、ショート動画を作ったり\n特殊メイクに挑戦してみる企画になりそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. If a movie is too difficult‚ they could make a short video‚\nor do a special effects makeup project.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0333286922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "雑誌の記事も、その撮影風景や、特殊メイクをして\n変わっていく様子をまとめるんじゃないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The magazine article would probably be about the filming process\nand how you transform with special effects makeup.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.4333286922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.4792015714
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "そっか……\nなら、ホラー系はやめておこうかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…\nThen I’ll pass on the horror genre.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.1125349047,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.445868238
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　千紗ちゃん、やってみたいって言ってたのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? But Chisa-chan‚ you said you wanted to do it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.445868238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.3791949592
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "やってみたいけど、ホラーが苦手なファンの人は\n記事が読み辛いんじゃないかなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I do‚ but I thought fans who don’t like horror\nmight have a hard time reading the article.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.5026131147,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "自分のやりたいことも大事だけど\nまずは、ファンの人達に喜んでもらいたいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My own desires are important‚\nbut first and foremost‚ I want to make my fans happy‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.5458570483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.7689664625
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "そっか。千紗ちゃんはファンの人達のことを\nとっても大切に想ってるんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Chisa-chan really cares\nabout her fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.8125267667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.4791934333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "だって、私がこれまで頑張ってこれたのは\n応援してくれるファンの人達のおかげだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s because of my fans who support me\nthat I’ve been able to work so hard until now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.6458601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.6458601
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "『ひたむきに頑張る姿を見て勇気をもらった』、とか\n『見ていて応援したくなる』、とか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They write things like‚ “Seeing you work so hard gave me courage‚”\nor “You make me want to cheer for you”…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.2125267667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "アンケートとか、お手紙に書いてもらって……\n読んだ私の方が勇気をもらっちゃったりして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And they write those things in questionnaires and letters…\nand I’m the one who ends up being encouraged by reading them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.4125226977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.1125226977
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "いつも、少しでもお返し出来たらいいなって\n思いながら、頑張ってるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I always do my best‚ hoping that I can give back\nto them even a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
