      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs026.m4a",
      "text": "え……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 353.2606211112,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "SNSが、感想で一杯になっちゃうくらい\nいいライブになったら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it’s a good enough live show to fill up social media\nwith reviews‚ and if it becomes a great live show‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 357.8145860878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "会場には来れなくても\n見つけた時、嬉しいんじゃないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "even if she can’t come to the venue‚\nshe’ll be happy when she finds out about it‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 361.6939391857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs027.m4a",
      "text": "っ……うん……うん、そうだね……\nありがとう、渚ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah… You’re right…\nThank you‚ Nagisa-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 370.1939391857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs028.m4a",
      "text": "（そうだよね……頑張らなきゃ……）\n（ファンの人達と、お姉ちゃんに、届くように……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（That’s right… I have to do my best…）\n（So that it reaches the fans and Saki-chan…!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 376.6939391857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、さくらちゃんがこの前\nソロでライブしてたし、話を聞いてみるのもいいかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ Sakura-chan did a solo live show recently‚\nmaybe it would be good to ask her about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 383.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_51_01-chs029.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんも、不安とかあったのかな……\nありがとう、ちょっと聞いてみるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if Sakura-chan was nervous too…\nThanks‚ I’ll ask her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 391.8939391857,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}